text: Mateusz Luty (born 1 January 1990) is a Polish bobsledder. He competed in the two-man event at the 2018 Winter Olympics. ==References== Category:1990 births Category:Living people Category:Polish male bobsledders Category:Olympic bobsledders of Poland Category:Bobsledders at the 2018 Winter Olympics Category:People from Lower Silesian Voivodeship
